## CRITICAL RULES (Violations Will Fail Review)

### 1. Technology Stack (MANDATORY)
✅ **MUST USE**:
- TypeScript strict mode (no `any` without justification)
- Tailwind CSS for all styling
- React Server Components by default
- Named exports: `export function ComponentName()`
- React 19 APIs: `useActionState`, `useFormStatus`, `useOptimistic`
- Radix UI for interactive primitives

❌ **FORBIDDEN**:
- jQuery (no `$`, no `jQuery`)
- Bootstrap (no `btn-*`, no `col-*`, no `container`)
- CSS modules, styled-components, Emotion
- Class components
- Default exports for components
- `any` type
- Inline styles (`style={{}}`)
- `console.log` in production code

### 2. Component Rules
```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT
'use client'; // Only if needed for hooks/events

import { type ComponentProps } from 'react';

interface ProductCardProps {
  product: Product;
  onAddToCart?: (productId: string) => void;
}

export function ProductCard({ product, onAddToCart }: ProductCardProps) {
  return (
    <div className="rounded-lg border bg-card p-4">
      {/* content */}
    </div>
  );
}
```

```tsx
// ❌ WRONG - Multiple violations
export default function ProductCard(props: any) {  // default export, any type
  return (
    <div style={{ padding: 16 }} className="container">  // inline style, Bootstrap
      <button class="btn btn-primary">Add</button>  // class not className, Bootstrap
    </div>
  );
}
```

### 3. Server vs Client Components

**Server Component (default)** - No directive needed:
- Static content
- Data fetching
- No event handlers
- No browser APIs

**Client Component** - Add `'use client'` at top:
- `onClick`, `onChange`, `onSubmit` handlers
- `useState`, `useEffect`, `useRef`
- `useFormStatus`, `useActionState`
- Browser APIs (localStorage, window, document)

### 4. ISML to JSX Conversion

| ISML | React 19 JSX |
|------|--------------|
| `<isif condition="${pdict.show}">` | `{show && <Component />}` |
| `<iselse>` | Ternary: `{condition ? <A /> : <B />}` |
| `<isloop items="${pdict.items}" var="item">` | `{items.map((item) => <Item key={item.id} />)}` |
| `<isinclude template="path/comp"/>` | `import { Comp } from '@/components/path/Comp'` |
| `<isdecorate template="layout">` | Layout component wrapping |
| `<isprint value="${val}" encoding="htmlcontent"/>` | Direct JSX: `{val}` |
| `<isset name="x" value="${y}" scope="page"/>` | Variable assignment: `const x = y` |
| `${pdict.variable}` | Props: `{variable}` |
| `<isscript>` | Move logic to component or utility |
| `<isslot>` | Children pattern: `{children}` |

### 5. Bootstrap to Tailwind Conversion

| Bootstrap | Tailwind |
|-----------|----------|
| `container` | `mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4` |
| `row` | `flex flex-wrap -mx-4` or `grid grid-cols-12 gap-4` |
| `col-md-6` | `w-full md:w-1/2 px-4` or `md:col-span-6` |
| `col-lg-4` | `w-full lg:w-1/3 px-4` or `lg:col-span-4` |
| `btn btn-primary` | `rounded-md bg-primary px-4 py-2 text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90` |
| `btn btn-secondary` | `rounded-md bg-secondary px-4 py-2 text-secondary-foreground` |
| `btn btn-outline-*` | `rounded-md border border-input bg-background px-4 py-2 hover:bg-accent` |
| `card` | `rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm` |
| `card-body` | `p-6` |
| `card-title` | `text-lg font-semibold` |
| `form-control` | `flex h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-input bg-background px-3 py-2` |
| `form-group` | `space-y-2` |
| `form-label` | `text-sm font-medium` |
| `alert alert-danger` | `rounded-md bg-destructive/10 p-4 text-destructive` |
| `alert alert-success` | `rounded-md bg-green-50 p-4 text-green-800` |
| `modal` | Radix Dialog component |
| `dropdown` | Radix DropdownMenu component |
| `carousel` | Custom component or embla-carousel |
| `collapse` | Radix Collapsible or Accordion |
| `d-none` | `hidden` |
| `d-md-block` | `hidden md:block` |
| `text-center` | `text-center` (same) |
| `text-muted` | `text-muted-foreground` |
| `mb-3` | `mb-3` (Tailwind uses same scale) |
| `py-4` | `py-4` (same) |

### 6. jQuery to React Conversion

| jQuery | React 19 |
|--------|----------|
| `$('#id')` | `useRef` or query in effect |
| `$(el).on('click', fn)` | `onClick={fn}` |
| `$(el).addClass('x')` | State: `className={active ? 'x' : ''}` |
| `$(el).removeClass('x')` | State toggle |
| `$(el).toggleClass('x')` | `setActive(prev => !prev)` |
| `$(el).attr('x', val)` | Props or state |
| `$(el).val()` | Controlled input: `value={state}` |
| `$(el).html(str)` | `dangerouslySetInnerHTML` (avoid) or proper JSX |
| `$(el).text(str)` | Direct JSX: `{str}` |
| `$(el).show()` / `.hide()` | Conditional render or `hidden` class |
| `$(el).fadeIn()` / `.fadeOut()` | CSS transitions with state |
| `$(el).slideUp()` / `.slideDown()` | CSS transitions or Radix Collapsible |
| `$.ajax({ url, method, data })` | Server Action or `fetch` |
| `$.get(url)` | `fetch(url)` in loader |
| `$.post(url, data)` | Server Action |
| `$(document).ready(fn)` | `useEffect` with empty deps |
| `$(el).find(sel)` | Component composition |
| `$(el).parent()` | Props/context |
| `$(el).closest(sel)` | Context or composition |
| `$('form').serialize()` | `FormData` from event |
| `$('form').submit()` | Form action |
| `$(el).trigger('event')` | Callback props or context |
| `$.fn.plugin()` | Custom hook or component |

